	<p style="text-align: left;">Hello Pocahontas County Families:</p>
<p>Pocahontas County Schools will be distributing 5 day meal packages on Monday April 6th. All Sites are pick-up only. Please remain inside your vehicle and a volunteer will place your package inside your trunk. Hillsboro Elementary will be from 10-12. Marlinton Elementary will be from 10:30 to 12:30, and Green Bank Elementary will be from 11-1. There will be an additional delivery to Linwood Library parking lot. If your child needs to be on the Linwood list, please call Sue Owen for a delivery time at 572-3333. Thank you.</p>
